data.description: Updated 2 bedrooms, 2 baths stepless condo features open family room with fireplace and laminate flooring throughout RM and dinning room. Tile floors in kitchen and bathrooms. Newer carpet in bedrooms. Sunroom feature tile floor to ceiling windows and view to walkout private balcony. Swim and tennis community. Convenient Smyrna location to 1-75 7 I-285. Will not last Long!
